Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是记录媒体的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是旧式的 但应该没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以复原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许其中记录着我们没有见过的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 可以了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是说过会带我参观加尔刚蒂亚的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近哥很忙 没这个闲工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎么这么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都在火海中和我互许终生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 和你这种野蛮泼辣的妹子比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔端庄的小姐更是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 拆除之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 映出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我们的机器还是第一次读出如此详细的数据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是设计图 或者是操纵手册吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人形机器人不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以技术水平来看 这东西和Chamber更为接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗机器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作这东西的人们走向了宇宙 并最终构筑了银河同盟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便离开了冻结的地球 他们仍旧没有放弃斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可悲 但这确实是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须从中吸取教训 避免重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到库盖尔舰团上也有这么棒的店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能消停点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这些料理加尔刚蒂亚上可都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没有点这么多的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会负责吃光的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？啊…是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出远门的时候我都会坐这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛真的很喜欢机械之类的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼欧都想把她挖走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候是情不自禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还去看了Chamber的驾驶舱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…也是情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还开着潜水人形机器人去救雷德了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…别再说这个话题了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是大家太搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的菜过会儿呈上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还打算吃那么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没办法跑来跑去和长时间运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我天生心脏就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也没法治疗 所以我只能去适应它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有姐姐陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有医生 雷德和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真坚强呢 贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你也很坚强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 你在一个陌生的地方开始了生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却像这样交到了朋友 工作着 活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很弱小 但却都很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 莉玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说要先回一趟自己的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是想要洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟今天天气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也回去洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧抓捕对象 把他带走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了 我们的目的是让雷德协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔到底有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能否驾驭这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不弄清楚 就无法将它用于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的知识对我们而言是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用强只会适得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已在捕获Striker驾驶员的行动中失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本国应该已经很不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的死亡是计划之外的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下 应该认为新对象的出现是一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得想办法让雷德自己离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的方针不变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果本国翻脸就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不单单是我们 就连这机体也保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你报告一下目前的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民们似乎相当劳累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为接收的前库盖尔舰团人员安排居住地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和维修船只的工作还在继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物资不足这点也很让人担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天虽然从商船那里补充了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为人员增加 所以消费也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光只是时间问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小零件和电池都搞不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各个公会都很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长 希望你能采取一些对策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地方 短缺的用品应该都可以得到补充
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说休闲设施也都很完善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是舰团长莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事需要向大家宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始 加尔刚蒂亚将前往海上货易据点 通称龙宫城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 龙宫城是什么地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各船主们及各公会制定好物资采购计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 我们也充分考虑了居民的慰劳问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是龙宫城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大规模的设施竟然能漂浮在海面上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 好多海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂 纱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是第一次这么近距离看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 玩个痛快吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔没办法来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么大的地方逛来逛去 对他的身体负担太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他说去帮奥尔德姆医生调查东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他买点礼物回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢各位提交计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会据此来进行贸易谈判的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从同行那里听说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里铁之类的物资好像全都涨价了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔬菜种子和谷物好像也都被买断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 我们出售的东西也可以卖个好价钱喽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是行情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就乘机赚上一笔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为什么是这个时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和陆地的动向有关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和陆地有关？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详情还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可以确定的是有部分物资流向了陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要时刻关注陆地各国的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他们接下来会有新的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和龙宫城高层见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会旁敲侧击一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 陆地吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相当可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办 头领
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然对这游乐园没啥兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但调查一下也没什么坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像祭典一样呢 莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 要试试看那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个去打想要的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个 像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑一个喜欢的打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意没装子弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海豚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 有好多的海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海洋哺乳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经离开海洋 后来又回到海中生活的物种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要选择这样的进化之路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到海中的它们 现在到底在追求什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像可以和海豚一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和海豚…一起玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳装都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳装是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啦 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米也准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿内衣不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件很适合莉玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 不错 不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 这件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面也有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人羡慕嫉妒恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得艾米他们真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这么开心的事我从来都没有经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你在那个库盖尔舰团嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么心事就和我们说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是同伴也是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想 要是能像那样和哥哥一起玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原来有哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舰团上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得帅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所需要的物资 我们应该都能够提供
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大舰团加尔刚蒂亚能停泊敝城 我们也是与有荣焉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们出售的商品也十分丰富 可以说是一次互惠互利的贸易
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分物资的流动存在偏向的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只是我杞人忧天 这下心里就踏实了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的消息还真是灵通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们而言 每一位客户都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不会厚此薄彼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最新的世界地图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面也标记了各势力的分布情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我们表示友好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知几位之后是否方便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必接受我们的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个好像不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着就像能做出各种各样的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就选这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 你们都在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见啊 你们会来这种店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品味不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在给贝贝尔买礼物 正打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子们就老老实实地回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是大人的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的时间算什么玩意儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢败坏风气 我可不会轻饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉吉特船长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了防止居民给龙宫城添麻烦 我正在看守！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊…喝多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让她喝的啊！这样子简直太糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我们要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就两个大老粗去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你说的 当然是现找一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 可以还给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚夺走的我的那颗心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这样儿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 莉玛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本国那边已经开始做回收准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在部队到达之前没有达成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动就会被终止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 他们打算把马兹尔也舍弃掉吗？这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高机密的兵器不能再这样放置于国外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面应该是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们最害怕的就是情报被泄露给敌国了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我想办法压下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一会儿就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械自行解析并运用语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是遗失的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会说话的机器…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Chamber那样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是像它那样的人工智能的前身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连这种东西都造出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不更深入地和人类交流 就无法度过严酷的冰河期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人形机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那个设计图里的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 我希望你能来我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助我研究这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.14,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,检测到了生命体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔 我可能会让你置身险境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.87,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像记录中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 还是不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.94,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,影像记录中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我无法理解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我开动了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有这一条路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我却开始讨厌战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了？要单独和我谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能帮我说服雷德 让他离开加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我不懂 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然还有艾米和贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望雷德 艾米和贝贝尔跟我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去哪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？莉玛你是陆地人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾米来的话 雷德肯定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是觉得不能丢下你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能离开加尔刚蒂亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地上也许有办法治好贝贝尔的病
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次见到陆地上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人告诉过我 不要和陆地人有所瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到莉玛是陆地人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.36,0:24:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使她说让我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是移居到陌生的地方这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.59,0:24:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果能治好贝贝尔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.92,0:24:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果治不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让那孩子陷入危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.17,0:24:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4点钟方向有舰团正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.78,0:25:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.26,0:25:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.18,0:25:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有见过的船影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海贼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.58,0:25:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让护卫舰出动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.36,0:26:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.32,0:26:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.46,0:26:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没赶上吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究还是打算来硬的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不通知我们一声就现身
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.21,0:26:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明已经把我们连同行动一起放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.16,0:26:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.09,0:26:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.63,0:26:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要抓到雷德 就是我们说的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.14,0:26:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃掉莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.33,0:26:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出发
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.12,0:26:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告接近中的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.79,0:26:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是加尔刚蒂亚舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.81,0:26:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告知贵舰团的所属以及行动目的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.54,0:26:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长 那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.42,0:26:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像不是海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:26:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚开始就一直以现在的距离和我们并行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.03,0:27:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.62,0:27:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的警戒对象都没有装备连接器
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.70,0:27:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗用的船只…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.20,0:27:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝罗兹 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.05,0:27:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.21,0:27:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 你知道什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.61,0:27:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接近的舰团到底是什么来历？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是从陆地而来的特务舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.22,0:27:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.56,0:27:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前说过 陆地上也许能治好贝贝尔的病
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.95,0:27:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也会被迫过上比疾病更痛苦的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.88,0:27:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.07,0:27:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隐瞒了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.09,0:27:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.30,0:27:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是卡奇纳斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.34,0:27:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.54,0:27:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.03,0:27:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.70,0:27:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.56,0:27:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.88,0:27:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被突然出现的两个男人抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.70,0:27:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然自作主张！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.68,0:27:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.01,0:27:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.77,0:27:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在之前去过的那家食堂附近
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.69,0:28:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.63,0:28:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.42,0:28:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的目标是你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.68,0:28:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.82,0:28:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.01,0:28:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你被抓的话就无法回到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.09,0:28:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去说服他们把艾米带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.16,0:28:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.42,0:28:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄刻阿诺斯号 紧急联络！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:19.25,ruby,NTP,0,300,0,,Oceanus
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.31,0:28:19.25,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：希腊神话中大洋河的河神
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.91,0:28:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米被抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.30,0:28:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.88,0:28:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个有精神的小姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.82,0:28:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.20,0:28:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻释放人质！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.82,0:28:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.35,0:28:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在可是我们的生命线
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.11,0:28:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以这女孩的生命为筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.47,0:29:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对象就会帮忙帮到底的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.35,0:29:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.77,0:29:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然特务舰队已经现身
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.95,0:29:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明一切都迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.79,0:29:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划已经被放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.25,0:29:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么就是不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.78,0:29:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只管完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.78,0:29:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.53,0:29:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.05,0:29:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.57,0:29:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西果然不是人形机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.58,0:29:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 这到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们称它为强化外装
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:52.41,ruby,NTP,250,0,0,,Augmented body
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫马兹尔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.80,0:29:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的同伴在驾驶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.26,0:29:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.95,0:30:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.20,0:30:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是同伴 是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.35,0:30:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是无人机
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.88,0:30:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.80,0:30:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮击？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.10,0:30:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面来电
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.61,0:30:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰队的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是歼灭正在脱离贵舰团的船舶 人员以及装备
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.10,0:30:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该船舶属于我国
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望贵舰团不要进行妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.30,0:30:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法认可
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.97,0:30:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两船上都确认到了本舰团的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.44,0:30:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请终止攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我国的正当权利 贵舰团已处在我军的舰炮射程内
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.83,0:30:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.97,0:30:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵舰团的阻挠行为 我们将以武力加以排除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.22,0:30:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 不能放任居民的安全受到威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.31,0:31:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰做好攻击准备 强化警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.35,0:31:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰请开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.31,0:31:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 乘上来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.76,0:31:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了艾米 我无论如何都必须保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.33,0:31:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.53,0:31:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾想把你卷进陆地上已经历时几百年的国与国的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.79,0:31:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了获取胜利 我曾想利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在我已经做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.59,0:31:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有权利破坏你们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.17,0:31:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.66,0:31:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乘上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.54,0:32:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非战斗人员请撤到舰团左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.86,0:32:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复 非战斗人员请撤到舰团左舷！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.46,0:32:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别推我！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.80,0:32:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别推！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.96,0:32:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.35,0:32:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人不在我们的射程内
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边推进边警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.22,0:32:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到敌人大型舰开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各护卫舰 做好迎击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.36,0:32:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认两侧交差着弹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.71,0:32:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离已经被对方测量到了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.26,0:32:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.46,0:32:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.11,0:32:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护卫舰允许应战
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.83,0:33:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.41,0:33:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.72,0:33:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.98,0:33:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去避难！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.80,0:33:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.31,0:33:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:32.58,ruby,NTP,0,180,0,,Adios
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.14,0:33:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.76,0:33:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头领
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.20,0:33:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集情报辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.05,0:33:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜此所赐 我下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.68,0:33:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.62,0:34:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.11,0:34:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.28,0:34:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没见过这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.73,0:34:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西正在扩张控制系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.35,0:34:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.94,0:34:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.39,0:34:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从来没发生过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.26,0:34:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能开得动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.75,0:34:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.18,0:34:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像它的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.52,0:34:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.27,0:34:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在脑海里描绘出你想做的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.18,0:34:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你想让这家伙做的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.72,0:34:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这东西的机制和Chamber一样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.65,0:34:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它应该能领会的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.15,0:35:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到那个地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.23,0:36:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.77,0:36:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保镖工作关门大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.65,0:36:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去做海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.43,0:36:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在不想和陆地那边扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.46,0:36:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 唯有这次不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.19,0:36:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹个痛快 就当是离舰声明了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.63,0:36:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.26,0:36:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别停歇！继续开炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.63,0:36:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电磁兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.94,0:37:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.37,0:37:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.59,0:37:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.80,0:37:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.63,0:37:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.48,0:37:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.65,0:37:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.37,0:37:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.47,0:37:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲着我来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.48,0:37:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着机体还没有流入他国 就先沉在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.13,0:37:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.23,0:37:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.67,0:37:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得赶紧离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.23,0:38:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在驾驶那东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.90,0:38:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.41,0:38:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没办法像雷德那么顺手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.60,0:38:21.14,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到操作机能显著下降 请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.93,0:38:30.01,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.77,0:38:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样吗？还是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.93,0:38:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.80,0:39:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.56,0:39:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是部了不起的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.80,0:39:52.61,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认搭乘者的生体情报以及机体的损坏状况
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.35,0:39:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果很多部像你这样的机械都能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.83,0:39:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切就都会乱套
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.19,0:40:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说是战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.70,0:40:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连生存之地都会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.87,0:40:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 我应该早点让你回归海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.10,0:40:14.04,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,将搭乘者认定为专属驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.51,0:40:21.35,mazul,NTP,0,0,0,,将机能维持更新为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.91,0:40:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.04,0:40:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.85,0:41:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔…Sys…tem
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.02,0:41:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.54,0:41:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是操作界面
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.70,0:41:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.80,0:42:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是马兹尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.57,0:42:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.17,0:42:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.30,0:42:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.76,0:42:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.85,0:42:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.78,0:42:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.76,0:42:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！你要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.37,0:42:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.24,0:42:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 等一下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.86,0:42:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹尔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.47,0:43:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.07,0:43:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.89,0:43:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.08,0:43:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.88,0:43:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 太好了 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.28,0:43:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那里别动 我现在就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.37,0:43:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已经不能回到加尔刚蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.05,0:43:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.97,0:43:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变成这样 都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.14,0:43:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个过错是不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.11,0:43:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟这些没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.31,0:43:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就别管这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.56,0:43:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言 马兹尔就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.98,0:44:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.18,0:44:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有回去的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.57,0:44:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.10,0:44:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得得救了 你却不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.70,0:44:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇 快带莉玛回来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.13,0:44:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要就此告辞 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.04,0:44:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇…诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.88,0:44:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那眼神 就像活着本身就已经是对你的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.29,0:44:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.50,0:44:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.84,0:44:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有接受这份罪行的觉悟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.59,0:44:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.20,0:45:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我用这种方法赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.68,0:45:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.88,0:45:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为海洋只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.02,0:45:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.70,0:45:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 长期以来的修复工作真是辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.60,0:46:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 加尔刚蒂亚又增加了一个新的生活据点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.65,0:46:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚我们所遭遇的身份不明的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.84,0:46:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是陆地国家所拥有的海上力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.92,0:46:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏护卫舰的奋斗以及各位的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.78,0:46:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得受害情况缩减到了最低
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.02,0:46:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎来了新的船只之后
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.25,0:46:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加尔刚蒂亚今后也必须是一个和平昌盛的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.10,0:46:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 请各位助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.11,0:46:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架机体确实和这东西连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.18,0:46:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地球上还有我所不知道的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.92,0:46:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.60,0:46:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛出生在战争连连的陆地上
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.73,0:46:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怎样生活下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.41,0:46:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是怀着怎样的心情看待我们的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.77,0:46:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.31,0:47:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.47,0:47:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛告诉过我 她不想破坏我们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.88,0:47:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管遇到怎样的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.08,0:47:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要在这里生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.21,0:47:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在这里保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.70,0:47:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
