Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:07.86,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}将聚散离合深埋心间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.74,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏出前进的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:21.88,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}记忆总以柔和的触感
