Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.66,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}与涛声的歌谣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:39.94,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自然而然的幸福满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:44.62,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们找到了开始的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:52.15,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}日出日落 冬去春来 世界不断变迁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.17,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们张开心的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:02:00.00,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}度过一天又一天的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:05.09,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论面对怎样的风向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:09.27,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}始终朝着自由的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:14.25,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:18.61,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为那悲伤的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:23.63,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}存在着绽放的光芒
